2S 2C 2H 2D 3S 3C 3H 3D 4S 4C 4H 4D 5S 5C 5H 5D 6S 6C 6H 6D 7S 7C 7H 7D 8S 8C 8H 8D 9S 9C 9H 9D JS JC JH JD QS QC QH QD KS KC KH KD AS AC AH AD
